If I don't. we'll get shot.

30
00:05:00.300 --> 00:05:02.510
Trouble! Trouble!

31
00:05:04.595 --> 00:05:05.763
Trouble!

32
00:05:07.557 --> 00:05:08.766
Trouble!

33
00:05:11.769 --> 00:05:13.646
Trouble! Trouble!

34
00:05:25.033 --> 00:05:28.161
Trouble! Trouble! Trouble!

35
00:05:31.706 --> 00:05:32.790
